short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Runs scripts to navigate to Canvas and import assignments into Assignmint.tech.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Stay on top of your assignments effortlessly with the AssignMint Chrome Extension. Designed to complement the AssignMint platform, this extension helps students streamline their workflow by integrating seamlessly with their browser.
